---
layout: base
title: 首頁
permalink: /
---

<section class="hero">
  <h1>歡迎來到 WhyBlog</h1>
  <p>這是一個使用 11ty、Markdown 和 GitHub Pages 建立的部落格</p>
</section>

<section class="recent-posts">
  <h2>最新文章</h2>
  <div class="post-grid">
    {% if collections.blog %}
      {% set posts = collections.blog | reverse %}
      {% for post in posts %}
        {% if loop.index <= 3 %}
        <div class="post-card">
          <h3><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h3>
          <time datetime="{{ post.date }}">{{ post.date | formatDate }}</time>
          {% if post.data.excerpt %}
            <div class="excerpt">{{ post.data.excerpt | safe }}</div>
          {% endif %}
          <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="read-more">繼續閱讀</a>
        </div>
        {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    {% else %}
      <p>暫無文章</p>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
</section>

<section class="recent-knowledge">
  <h2>最新知識庫文章</h2>
  <div class="post-grid">
    {% if collections.knowledge %}
      {% set posts = collections.knowledge | reverse %}
      {% for post in posts %}
        {% if loop.index <= 3 %}
        <div class="post-card">
          <h3><a href="{% if post.data.permalink %}{{ post.data.permalink }}{% else %}{{ post.url }}{% endif %}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h3>
          <time datetime="{{ post.date }}">{{ post.date | formatDate }}</time>
          {% if post.data.excerpt %}
            <div class="excerpt">{{ post.data.excerpt | safe }}</div>
          {% endif %}
          <a href="{% if post.data.permalink %}{{ post.data.permalink }}{% else %}{{ post.url }}{% endif %}" class="read-more">繼續閱讀</a>
        </div>
        {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    {% else %}
      <p>暫無文章</p>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
</section>
